- In the inspector window, go to the "Console" tab.
- Type `window.open("chrome://inspect/#devices")` in the console.
- Press Enter.

This will bring up the list of available devices for inspection in Chrome.

### 3. Execute JavaScript Directly
Sometimes, directly executing scripts from the command line works better than opening the developer tools:

```csharp
