### 1. Setup Your LaTeX Document

First, let's create a minimal LaTeX document:

```latex
\documentclass{book}
\usepackage[utf8]{inputenc}
\usepackage{hyperref} % For creating hyperlinks within the PDF

% Use ctex package for Chinese title formatting
